[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Neptune is still the monarch of the empire of the seas, and Pluto (although metamorphosed into the Devil) has retained the throne of Tartarus.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "They have both been more lucky than their brother Jupiter, who had to suffer specially the vicissitudes of fortune.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "All traces of the ex God were lost, and I have questioned in vain old chronicles and old women; no one has been able to furnish me with any information as to his destiny.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I am now convinced that the middle ages have not bequeathed to us any traditions concerning the fate of Jupiter after the fall of Paganism.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "All that I have been able to discover in connection with this subject is the history told me long ago by my friend Niels Andersen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I have just mentioned Niels Andersen, and this good figure, at once so droll and so lovable, emerges all riant in my memory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I must devote a few lines to him here.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "For the rest, I like to indicate my authorities and to show their good or bad qualities, in order that the reader may be in a position to judge himself how far these authorities deserve to be trusted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "It is to him that I am indebted for what knowledge I have of the whale fishery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "He taught me all the subtleties of the art; he made me acquainted with all the stratagems and dodges which the intelligent animal employs to baffle these subtle snares and make its escape.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "To him I owe all, and if I have not become a famous whaler the fault rests neither with Niels Andersen nor with myself, but with my evil star, which has never allowed me in the course of my life to encounter any whale with which I might have engaged in honorable combat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I have only encountered vulgar stockfish and miserable herrings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Of what use is the best harpoon when you have to deal with a herring?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Now that my limbs are paralysed I must renounce for ever the hope of pursuing whales.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Since then poor Niels Andersen went limping upon an artificial leg manufactured from one of the firs of his country, and which he extolled as a masterpiece of Norwegian carpentry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "He of course commenced with such a panegyric the legend we give here.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "He has a good character and much taste for conjugal life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "It is a touching sight,\" he added, \"to see a family of whales grouped around its venerable patriarch, and couched upon an enormous mass of ice, basking in the sun",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Sometimes the young ones begin to frisk and romp, and at length all plunge into the sea to play at hide and seek among the immense ice blocks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "\"I believe this is an error,\" I cried, interrupting my friend.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "These banquets of vermin at length trouble their involuntary host and even cause him excessive sufferings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Enormous as is the quantity of oil in the whale, it has not the least religious sentiment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "It is only among animals of mediocre stature that we find any religion; the very great, the creatures gigantic like the whale are not endowed with it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "What can be the reason?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Is it that they cannot find a church sufficiently spacious to afford them entrance into its pale?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Nor have the whales any taste for the prophets, and the one which swallowed jonah was not able to digest that great preacher; seized with nausea, it vomited him after three days.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Most certainly that proves the absence of all religious sentiment in these monsters.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "The whale, therefore, would never choose an ice block for prayer cushion, and sway itself in attitudes of devotion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000009_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000009_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "It adores as little the true God who resides above there in heaven, as the false pagan god who dwells near the arctic pole, in the Isle of the Rabbits, where the dear beast goes sometimes to pay him a visit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I am not able to give you its precise geographical position.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Since its first discovery no one has been able to visit it again; the enormous mountains of ice accumulated around it bar the approach.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "When these sailors, reached it with their ship they found it deserted and uncultivated.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Sickly stalks of broom swayed sadly upon the quicksands; here and there were scattered some dwarf shrubs and stunted firs crouching on the sterile soil.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000010_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000010_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "A cabin, the only one they discovered, announced the presence of a human being.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "His lineaments, though worn and ravaged, conserved traces of beauty; they were noble and perfectly regular.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "But you-what are you.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "But the old man could give them but scant information.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Nevertheless, he added that he felt much pleasure at this moment in speaking his native language, being Greek by birth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "He begged his compatriots to inform him as to the then state of Greece.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "The most singular thing was that none of the seamen knew the names of the towns concerning which he questioned them, and which, according to him, had been flourishing cities in his time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "\"The old man asked, with the most lively interest, and even with a certain anxiety, about an ancient temple, which, he said, had been of old the grandest in all Greece.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "None of his hearers recognised the name,, which he pronounced with tender emotion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "'The village where I was born,' he exclaimed, 'is situated precisely there.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "During my childhood I have long watched there the pigs of my father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "On this site there are, in fact, the ruins of very ancient constructions, which must have been incredibly magnificent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Here and there you see some columns still erect; they are isolated or connected by fragments of roofing, whence hang tendrils of honeysuckle and red bind weeds.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Other columns, some of them red marble, lie fractured on the grass.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "The ivy has invaded their superb capitals, formed of flowers and foliage delicately chiselled.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Great slabs of marble, squared fragments of wall and triangular pieces of roofing, are scattered about, half buried in the earth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000013_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000013_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Unfortunately these sculptures are much injured by time, and are covered with moss and creepers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "The bird at his side emitted terrible cries, spread its enormous wings, and menaced the strangers with talons and beak.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "The she goat moaned and licked the hands of her master, whose sorrows she seemed trying to comfort by her humble caresses.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "At this sight a strange trouble swelled in the hearts of the seamen; they hastily quitted the hut, and did not feel at ease until they could no more hear the sobbings of the old man, the croakings of the hideous bird, and the bleatings of the goat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "When they got on board their vessel again they related their adventures.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "Such was the history of Niels Andersen, and it made my heart bleed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7346/91900/7346_91900_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7346",
        "content": "I will not dissemble; already his revelations concerning the secret sufferings of the whale had profoundly saddened me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7346_91900_000015_000002",
